      public Item(String name, ArrayList<Tag> tags, String dateOfPurchase, double estimatedValue, String make, String model, String serialNumber, String description, String comment)
      Constructor of an Item object
      Parameters:
      name - the name of the item
      tags - stores a list of tags assigned to the item
      dateOfPurchase - the date of purchase/acquisition of the item
      estimatedValue - the estimated value of the item
      make - the make of the item
      model - the model of the item
      serialNumber - the serial number of the item (if applicable)
      description - the description of the item
      comment - the comment on the item
